Used to provide extra configuration to openssl (e.g. SubjectAltName).

Examples:
  KWM_PKI_NAME=test \\
  KWM_PKI_PATH=pki \\
  KWM_PKI_CA=MYCA \\
  KWM_PKI_SUBJ=/CN=test \\
  KWM_PKI_EXT="subjectAltName = IP:10.100.0.10,IP:54.30.20.10,DNS:cluster.domain.com" \\
    $SCRIPT_NAME render pki-create-signed-cert
